Indicators: ✔ - Supported. If an update added support, then the minimum required version appears in the footnote. • - Support for these releases is ending soon. Please upgrade as soon as possible. WARNING Anti-malware software, such as Deep Security Agent, must run in an unconfined domain in order to protect the whole computer. Any additional SELinux policy customization or configuration might block the agent. If any alerts occur, see Troubleshoot SELinux alerts.
